	(text_box "PCB Notes on L80\n1. It needs to be at least 5mm from the board edge\n2. Make a 3cm x 3cm around it with a solid ground plane\n3. Keep tall components at least 10mm away form it\n4. Place high speed components or high speed signal traces in the opposite side of the board"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
